Moonstone beach stones



Although the beach was filled with small sea-smoothed stones in all sorts of interesting colors,
we saw none of the driftglass I usually find in such piles.
Taken Sunday, June 24, 2001, 11:49:55am.  Original image size: 1200x1600, 972kb
Technical details: Olympus C700UZ, 1/250s @ F5.6, ISO 100, 38mm
